# obfuscator-ai

AI-powered code obfuscation utility.

## Installation

`ash
pip install obfuscator-ai
`

## Usage

`python
from obfuscator_ai import obfuscate

# Your code here
result = obfuscate(source_code)
`

## Command Line

`ash
obfuscator-ai input.py -o output.py
`
